<div id="s1a" class="bms-section bms-narrative mw-customtoggle-s1a">
<div class="bms-section-header bms-section-title-narrative">
<span class="bms-section-label">now i float numbly</span>
</div>
<div class="mw-collapsible mw-collapsed" id="mw-customcollapsible-s1a">
<div class="bms-narrative-inner">
[[File:abutterfly.png|class=bms-butterfly-deco|250px]]
[[File:abutterfly.png|class=bms-butterfly-deco-2|250px]]
<div class="bms-poem-block align-center">
My heartbeat messes up.
It messes up when I see him…
It races uncontrollably, I blush heavily!
Closing distance, thud, thud.
It's like I'm going to explode!
Butterflies in my stomach,
they fly freely.
Tingling my belly,
they seem to want to get out,
but just can't.
Until I'm face to face,
chest to chest.
His heat can be felt in my skin,
slowly pressing,
slowly accepting its embrace.
The butterflies free into the sky!
They dance brightly in a quiet bay,
spreading their wings.
The ceiling was no limit
to what they could reach!
As beautiful as his face.
I fade into a beautiful dark while holding tight.
So tight it marks my skin, with his relief.
I would be like this forever…
<span class="bms-scream">If it weren't fake.</span>
I count them, aching.
They're bigger, round, purple.
<span class="bms-scream">They hurt, hurt, hurt!</span>
His embrace left my body tainted.
Left me hurting, pained.
<span class="bms-staccato">Where is it, where is it?</span>
I search in my room, in the dark.
</div>
[[File:redsuprise.png|class=bms-slash-deco|250px]]
<span class="bms-ellipsis">…</span>
<div class="bms-poem-block align-center">
I found it.
</div>
<span class="bms-ellipsis">…</span>
<div class="bms-poem-block align-center">
<span class="bms-whisper">Please work again.</span>
<span class="bms-staccato">Swallow, swallow, swallow.</span>
Down my esophagus, into my veins.
It's integrated into my roots,
the aftertaste is a cascade.
</div></div>

