</div>
</div>

<div class="bms-section bms-narrative mw-customtoggle-s1i">
<div class="bms-section-header bms-section-title-narrative">
<span class="bms-section-label">……</span>
</div>
<div class="mw-collapsible mw-collapsed" id="mw-customcollapsible-s1i">
<div class="bms-narrative-inner">
<div class="bms-poem-block align-left">
The door closed again.
</div>
<span class="bms-ellipsis">…</span>
<div class="bms-poem-block align-left">
What now?
I just wonder,
why Dream Wine?
It was so dumb to hope!
It was so hurting to watch!
I can't. I can't. I can't!
The bottle alone.
The butterfly eggs!
A deep breath.
A superficial breath.
Readying my tongue.
Umami and drug down my throat!
</div>
<div class="bms-cascade-block">
<span>Just forget</span>
<span>and melt</span>
<span>into the sweet</span>
<span>sweet</span>
<span>aroma of the</span>
<span>champagne-tasting</span>
<span>ever-shifting</span>
<span>concrete-like</span>
<span>chlorinated wine</span>
<span>and</span>
<span>enjoy!</span>
</div>
<div class="bms-poem-block align-left">
Because there's no need to fight
for what pierced and skinned and mutilated.
How will this dream begin, end?
I'll keep your promise and
just make my corpse melt!
Everything down, the bottle dry.
</div>
<div class="bms-poem-block align-center">
I feel so beautiful?!
</div>
</div>

<div class="bms-section bms-drug mw-customtoggle-s2e">
